  "problemSolved": {
    "statement": "MiroFlow is a high-performance, modular framework for building intelligent AI agents that deliver state-of-the-art results on complex reasoning tasks like future event prediction. The framework features advanced multi-turn conversation capabilities, extensive tool ecosystem integration, and hierarchical sub-agent orchestration for optimal task completion. Learn more about our [agent framework](https://miromindai.github.io/MiroFlow/core_concepts/).",
